&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6281/928e29ff96b06ac209c56baaa5cf19f4_1200x700.jpg?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1200x700-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;343&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
